name: The Horseman
description:
One of the Indonesia famous dance from East Java named Kuda Lumping. Kuda Lumping Dance has unique performance, with colorful ornament paint on the bamboo woven horse. 
     
     The Series of Indonesia Art Culture (From Rejoice The Elder, Leap Into The Sky, Dance with Leak, The Dancer, Bali Dancer, Yudhistira Lost in Space & Shinta Dance).
